%   https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Windows-1252
%   https://stackoverflow.com/questions/270672/unicode-in-postscript
% With help from KenS, with 4 corrections to his encoding vector:
%   https://stackoverflow.com/questions/32443178/how-do-i-encode-a-font-to-use-cp1252-windows-1252-encoding-in-postscript
